@jwpeterson seems you wrote a lot of the GMSH reader. Do you know how nodesets should be created in Gmsh to be loaded into libMesh as nodesets?
@burritotukituki if the shape of the nodeset is simple enough, you can define it in MOOSE instead with the mesh generators
https://mooseframework.inl.gov/syntax/Mesh/index.html
Guillaume
